    "caption": "板嘴山巨嘴鸟，厄瓜多尔",
    "title": "板嘴山巨嘴鸟与兰花，厄瓜多尔",
    "description": "拥有如多功能工具般的喙部和色彩斑斓的羽毛——板嘴山巨嘴鸟（Plate-billed mountain toucan）是安第斯山脉最具辨识度的鸟类之一。它栖息在厄瓜多尔和哥伦比亚西南部潮湿的山地森林中，已完全适应了林冠层高处的生存环境。",
    "copyright": "© Murray Cooper/Minden Pictures",
    "date": "2026 7月 7",
    "clickUrl": "/search?q=%e6%9d%bf%e5%98%b4%e5%b1%b1%e5%b7%a8%e5%98%b4%e9%b8%9f&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate:\"20260706_1600\"",
    "imageUrls": {
      "landscape": {
        "highDef": "/th?id=OHR.MountainToucanOrchids_ZH-CN1400221431_1920x1080.jpg",
        "ultraHighDef": "/th?id=OHR.MountainToucanOrchids_ZH-CN1400221431_UHD.jpg",
        "wallpaper": "/th?id=OHR.MountainToucanOrchids_ZH-CN1400221431_1920x1200.jpg"
